dc_creator_sm: Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner, Composite Atlas of France.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Includes French coat of arms and the face of a cherubim on the title cartouche. From the Composite Atlas of France, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 48 x 36 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
